{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_11", "eventName": "淬火塵霾", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "11-14", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "一場相見", "storyInfo": "指揮塔上方，阿米婭、Logos及阿斯卡綸對戰血魔大君與曼弗雷德，雙方相持不下。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_victoria", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true", "initamount": 0.0, "amount": 0.7, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "四年前"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與薩卡茲相比，時間總是在你們的個體與國家身上走得很快。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "名為高盧的巨人倒下之後，維多利亞與萊塔尼亞瘋狂地吸收著它的遺骸。不過幾十年而已，屬於高盧的時代就已經遠去。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不曾見過科西嘉一世的戰艦與火炮。你不曾感受過林貢斯的繁華與驕傲。你父輩的領地如今早已淪為維多利亞邊境貴族的轄地。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你穿著維多利亞的高級軍官制服，身上掛滿了維多利亞授予的勳章。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你說著標準的倫蒂尼姆貴族圈慣用的維多利亞語，甚至不帶有絲毫高盧口音。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你走到我面前，聲稱自己要與薩卡茲談判時，你憑什麼自稱“高盧人”？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......攝政王殿下，如今沒有一座城市屬於那個名為高盧的國家。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "站在您面前的，並不是一名高盧人，而是高盧遺民。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們有的身處維多利亞，有的身處哥倫比亞，有的身處萊塔尼亞。並非我們選擇流浪，而是早就沒有一個地方可被稱作故鄉。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們想重建高盧？", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。就像您和其他薩卡茲想要重建卡茲戴爾一樣。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩百年前，高盧帝國的炮兵團也曾圍在卡茲戴爾的城牆下。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而此時此刻，你竟然將自己與薩卡茲相提並論。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "參與那場對卡茲戴爾戰爭的也有維多利亞。而我聽說您與軍事委員會之所以能進入倫蒂尼姆，正是受到卡文迪許公爵的邀請。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你也一定聽說過他的下場。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十天前，斯塔福德公爵在倫蒂尼姆掀起了一場叛亂，卡文迪許公爵為阻止斯塔福德公爵的陰謀挺身而出。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆城防軍參與了那場戰鬥，很遺憾，斯塔福德公爵與卡文迪許公爵都沒能從飛向彼此的炮彈下活著走出來。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您一定比我更清楚，其他公爵正熱切地關注著倫蒂尼姆內部的局勢。無論您之後準備在城內做什麼，您都需要新的幫手。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你與薩卡茲合作的方式。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。如您所見，高盧遺民會全力支持卡茲戴爾軍事委員會在倫蒂尼姆的一切行動。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們所希望的，只是在之後維多利亞的亂局中，讓那幾座原本屬於高盧的城市回到高盧。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_062"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我答應你又如何？一個國家的興亡與其擁有的城市數量毫無瓜葛。", "name": "特雷西斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_062"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道，攝政王殿下。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#9$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是......我們已經等不到什麼更好的時機了。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認識一名青年近衛軍，他曾在直屬於高盧皇帝本人的帝國衛隊服役。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我認識他的時候，他已經六十多歲了。但帝國衛隊早已在四皇會戰中灰飛煙滅，所以他一輩子都成不了老近衛軍。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他對我說起過意氣風發的皇帝，戰無不勝的艦隊，行軍路上的笑談。幾十年來，他堅持使用高盧語一遍遍地講述這些故事。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#8$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他如今正躺在倫蒂尼姆切普區的一間狹小的療養院裡。我最近一次去見他的時候，他已經快忘記如何說話。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即便如此，每天看到電視上出現帝政風格的建築時，他渾濁的眼睛還是會恢復神采，痙攣的雙手依然會忍不住抬起來鼓掌。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而不出五年，他就會死去。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後一代親眼見過高盧的高盧人正在死去。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#7$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攝政王殿下，您說得對。與薩卡茲相比，我們的壽命太微不足道，我們的記憶......也無法透過血脈來傳承。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等最後一代親歷者死去，我們對高盧的回憶就會和那個帝國一樣隨風而散，到了那個時候，高盧就會真正消失。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們唯一能做的，就是盡可能抓住這些餘燼。", "name": "萊托中校"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_649_1#2$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g6_controltower_street", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "弩炮發射！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 8.0, "ystrength": 6.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "守住封閉層，別讓他們繼續靠近！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城防軍士兵的鬥志很頑強。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為他們的長官還在上面。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些士兵......的確很尊敬那位指揮官。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "指揮官，薩卡茲來了！羅德島的幹員們正在與他們交戰！", "name": "自救軍戰士"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_398_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "支援他們。我們需要在正面戰場上盡可能地吸引敵人的注意，來為博士的行動爭取時間。", "name": "克洛維希婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_401_1#6$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "32_g7_controltower", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$manfri_01_intro", "key": "$manfri_01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "海布里區的雇傭兵大概死在你的手上。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "戰爭近在眼前。你我心知肚明。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "阿斯卡綸"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_395_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿斯卡綸，你生在卡茲戴爾，長在卡茲戴爾，將軍把你從死人堆裡抱出來，殿下教你如何握緊武器保護自己、保護家園。", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可在這個薩卡茲最需要團結一致的時刻，你和羅德島那些薩卡茲在做什麼？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#6$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你準備把我們的情報交給維多利亞人嗎？交給......一群曾經踐踏過卡茲戴爾的異族人？", "name": "曼弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_404_1#2$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_circleatk_h", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.2, "b": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_circleatk_n"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "CameraShake", "at